# Build artifacts and the auto-healed lockfile for this standalone
# fixture workspace. Cargo.lock is ignored because its litmask path-dep
# pins the workspace version (e.g. 0.10.0), which `cargo set-version`
# does NOT reach across the workspace boundary — committing it would go
# stale on every release bump and dirty the tree on the next build.
/target
Cargo.lock
